7// DisplayImpl.cpp: Implementation methods of egl::Display
8
9#include "libANGLE/renderer/DisplayImpl.h"
10
11#include "libANGLE/Display.h"
12#include "libANGLE/Surface.h"
13
14namespace rx
15{
16
17DisplayImpl::DisplayImpl(const egl::DisplayState &state)
18 : mState(state), mExtensionsInitialized(false), mCapsInitialized(false), mBlobCache(nullptr)
19{}
20
21DisplayImpl::~DisplayImpl()
22{
23 ASSERT(mState.surfaceSet.empty());
24}
25
26egl::Error DisplayImpl::prepareForCall()
27{
28 return egl::NoError();
29}
30
31egl::Error DisplayImpl::releaseThread()
32{
33 return egl::NoError();
34}
35
36const egl::DisplayExtensions &DisplayImpl::getExtensions() const
37{
38 if (!mExtensionsInitialized)
39 {
40 generateExtensions(&mExtensions);
41 mExtensionsInitialized = true;
42 }
43
44 return mExtensions;
45}
46
47egl::Error DisplayImpl::handleGPUSwitch()
48{
49 return egl::NoError();
50}
51
52egl::Error DisplayImpl::validateClientBuffer(const egl::Config *configuration,
53 EGLenum buftype,
54 EGLClientBuffer clientBuffer,
55 const egl::AttributeMap &attribs) const
56{
57 UNREACHABLE();
58 return egl::EglBadDisplay() << "DisplayImpl::validateClientBuffer unimplemented.";
59}
60
61egl::Error DisplayImpl::validateImageClientBuffer(const gl::Context *context,
62 EGLenum target,
63 EGLClientBuffer clientBuffer,
64 const egl::AttributeMap &attribs) const
65{
66 UNREACHABLE();
67 return egl::EglBadDisplay() << "DisplayImpl::validateImageClientBuffer unimplemented.";
68}
69
70egl::Error DisplayImpl::validatePixmap(egl::Config *config,
71 EGLNativePixmapType pixmap,
72 const egl::AttributeMap &attributes) const
73{
74 UNREACHABLE();
75 return egl::EglBadDisplay() << "DisplayImpl::valdiatePixmap unimplemented.";
76}
77
78const egl::Caps &DisplayImpl::getCaps() const
79{
80 if (!mCapsInitialized)
81 {
82 generateCaps(&mCaps);
83 mCapsInitialized = true;
84 }
85
86 return mCaps;
87}
